    "body": "See https://github.com/electron/electron/issues/5830#issuecomment-243706205\nhttps://github.com/electron/electron/issues/673\n\nFor issues discussing this generic issue that others have faced.  The TLDR is that splitting `electron.exe` into `electron.dll` and `electron.exe` is quite difficult and not in the plan at the moment.  The runtime discussion is still ongoing.  Using the same executable for multiple programs introduces a whole heap of issues though.\n"
